<Title>Wing Midspan Fixed Trailing Edge Flex Panel Hinge Seals</Title>
<DispatchCondition>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>For model 787-9 or 787-10, up to six seals may be missing.  The most inboard seal on each wing may not be missing.</Para>
<Para>It should be noted that the Wing Midspan Fixed Trailing Edge Flex Panel Hinge Seals should not be confused with the Wing Inboard Fixed Trailing Edge Seals. The six seals on the wing inboard fixed trailing edge may not be missing.</Para>
<Para>Reduce performance limited weights for each missing seal by:</Para>
